  "settings_info_fork_title": "Why Aurora Pulse is developed as an independent product",
  "settings_info_fork_desc_1": "The origin is Aurora as a bit-perfect HiRes player. That strong foundation established the sound quality, local-first approach, and core product direction that Aurora Pulse builds on.",
  "settings_info_fork_desc_2": "Missing features and slower development cycles led to creating Aurora Pulse as a fork focused on faster releases, meaningful feature additions, and quicker issue resolution.",
  "settings_info_fork_desc_3": "The name Aurora Pulse intentionally signals forward development without losing the original roots. Both versions offer clear strengths, and we thank the original source code author for the work behind Aurora.",
  "settings_info_feature_list_title": "Key features",
