  "settings_info_ai_title": "AI-supported development process",
  "settings_info_ai_desc": "The app itself does not use AI features for end users. AI is used only in development to evaluate architecture and refactoring options faster, derive stronger test coverage, catch regressions earlier, and prepare code reviews more consistently. This improves code quality, consistency, and delivery speed across both new features and bug fixes. We currently use TRAE 3.5, GPT-5.3-Codex, and Gemini-3 Pro as supporting tools in engineering and quality assurance.",
